### Travel Bliss Backend - API Tests
### Bu faylni VSCode da REST Client extension bilan ishlatish mumkin

### 1. Server Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### 2. Root Endpoint
GET http://localhost:5000/

### 3. Backend Status
GET http://localhost:5000/api/demo/status

### 4. Get Demo Users
GET http://localhost:5000/api/demo/users

### 5. Create Demo User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/demo/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Aziz Rahimov",
  "email": "aziz@example.com",
  "phone": "+998901234570"
}

### 6. Delete Demo User (ID ni o'zgartiring)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/demo/users/1

### ================================================
### AUTH ENDPOINTS (MongoDB kerak)
### ================================================

### 7. Register New User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Javohir Akbarov",
  "email": "javohir@example.com",
  "phone": "+998901234567",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 8. Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "javohir@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 9. Get Current User Profile (Token kerak)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Update Password (Token kerak)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/update-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### 11. Update Profile (Token kerak)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/auth/update-profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Javohir Akbarov Yangi",
  "phone": "+998901234999"
}

### 12. Logout (Token kerak)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
